OL,3,CPothole compensation claims double in
OL,4,Ca year
OL,6,FThe number of pothole compensation
OL,7,Fclaims made to councils in Britain
OL,8,Fdoubled in a year, according to new
OL,9,Fanalysis.
OL,11,FRAC research found 20,432 claims were
OL,12,Fsubmitted to 18 local authorities with
OL,13,Fthe largest road networks in 2023,
OL,14,Fcompared with 8,327 in 2022.
OL,16,FOf the councils which provided data,
OL,17,FSurrey County Council saw the biggest
OL,18,Fincrease in claims, from 734 to 3,418.
