OL,6,FThe study also indicated that just 15%
OL,7,Fof claims made last year resulted in
OL,8,Fpay-outs.
OL,10,FIn Kent, 92 per cent of pothole
OL,11,Fcompensation claims were refused last
OL,12,Fyear. In 2023, 1884 claims were made
OL,13,Fin the county, more than double the
OL,14,Fprevious year.
OL,16,FKent County Council says it spends
OL,17,Fmore than fifty million pounds a year
OL,18,Fon repairs, but it still needs more
OL,19,Fgovernment funding.
