OL,6,FPayments averaged just #260 each,
OL,7,Fwhereas the RAC believes a typical
OL,8,Frepair bill for pothole damage beyond
OL,9,Fa puncture is #460.
OL,11,FCouncils refused seven out of 10
OL,12,Fclaims because they were not aware the
OL,13,Fpothole existed, which is permitted
OL,14,Funder the Highways Act 1980.
OL,16,FA driving instructor in Hampshire says
OL,17,Fhe has been left hundreds of pounds
OL,18,Fout of pocket after his car was
OL,19,Fdamaged by a pothole while with a
OL,20,Flearner on their way to a test.
