OL,6,FThe highest proportion of refusals
OL,7,Famong the local authorities included
OL,8,Fin the analysis was 98% by
OL,9,FGloucestershire County Council.
OL,11,FThe figures, obtained in response to
OL,12,FFreedom of Information requests, also
OL,13,Frevealed that 13 councils spent a
