OL,6,FRAC head of policy Simon Williams
OL,7,Fsaid: "These findings are a stark
OL,8,Freminder that the ongoing poor
OL,9,Fcondition of many of the UK's local
OL,10,Froads is burning holes in the budgets
OL,11,Fof both local authorities and drivers."
OL,13,FWhile some councils appeared to
OL,14,Fprioritise paying legal fees over
OL,15,Fsettling pothole claims, the cost in
OL,16,Ftime and money of defending claims
OL,17,Fappears to far outweigh the expense of
OL,18,Freimbursing drivers for the damage
OL,19,Fdone to their vehicle in the first
OL,20,Fplace."
