OL,6,FEven if a driver successfully pursued
OL,7,Fcompensation, the average sum paid out
OL,8,Fof #260 is often well below the cost
OL,9,Fto fix a pothole-damaged car, for
OL,10,Fanything more serious than a punctured
OL,11,Ftyre."
