OL,6,FHowever, this has become increasingly
OL,7,Fchallenging, with an estimated and
OL,8,Fgrowing #16.3 billion backlog of
OL,9,Frepairs to bring all local roads
OL,10,Facross the country up to scratch."Each
OL,11,Fclaim for compensation sent to a
OL,12,Fcouncil is robustly judged on its own
OL,13,Fmerits and in accordance to the law."
OL,15,FAll councils need greater, longer-term
